"This is Fantastic Island's default local profile. Import a YAML file or add a secure subscription when you want to replace it." = "這是 Fantastic Island 預設建立的本地設定檔。想替換它時，可以匯入 YAML 或新增安全的訂閱連結。";
"Built-in mode starts Mihomo automatically when needed. Settings only manages profiles and troubleshooting tools." = "內建模式會在需要時自動啟動 Mihomo。設定頁只負責設定檔管理與排障工具。";
"No Profile Yet" = "還沒有可用設定檔";
"Add a subscription or import a YAML file first. Fantastic Island will use the profile you mark as current." = "先新增訂閱或匯入 YAML。Fantastic Island 會使用你標記為目前的那條設定檔。";
"Refresh the remote YAML before Fantastic Island switches to this subscription." = "在 Fantastic Island 切換到這條訂閱之前，先刷新遠端 YAML。";
"Detect Mode" = "探測模式";
"Managed Mode" = "託管模式";
"Detection mode reads an existing Clash client through its local API and config path. Fantastic Island does not start or manage the runtime in this mode." = "探測模式會讀取你現有 Clash 客戶端的本地 API 與設定路徑。這個模式下 Fantastic Island 不會啟動或託管執行環境。";
"Managed mode keeps YAML profiles in Fantastic Island, syncs subscriptions, and starts the managed Mihomo runtime when assets are available." = "託管模式會把 YAML 設定保存在 Fantastic Island 裡，同步訂閱，並在需要時啟動內建的 Mihomo 執行環境。";
"Connection Mode" = "連接模式";
"Choose whether Fantastic Island should inspect an existing Clash client or manage its own Mihomo runtime." = "選擇讓 Fantastic Island 探測並接入現有 Clash 客戶端，還是由 Fantastic Island 自己託管 Mihomo 執行環境。";
"Connection" = "連接";
"Config" = "設定";
"Not set" = "未設定";
"No profile" = "未新增";
"Detection mode never starts Fantastic Island's managed Mihomo workflow. Use it when you already have another Clash client running and only want Fantastic Island to inspect or control that client." = "探測模式不會啟動 Fantastic Island 內建的 Mihomo。適合你已經有其他 Clash 客戶端在執行，只希望 Fantastic Island 讀取或控制那個客戶端時使用。";
"Managed mode uses Fantastic Island's profile library and managed Mihomo workflow. Use it when you want Fantastic Island to manage subscriptions and runtime behavior itself." = "託管模式會使用 Fantastic Island 自己的設定檔庫和內建 Mihomo。適合你希望把訂閱和執行環境行為都交給 Fantastic Island 管理時使用。";
"Detection Settings" = "探測設定";
"Point Fantastic Island at the Clash API and optional config file from the client you already use. Fantastic Island only reads and controls that existing runtime." = "把 Fantastic Island 指向你目前正在使用的 Clash API，以及可選的設定檔路徑。Fantastic Island 只會讀取與控制那個既有執行環境。";
"Managed Profiles" = "託管設定";
"Add, rename, delete, and switch the YAML profiles that Fantastic Island can run in managed mode." = "在這裡新增、重新命名、刪除並切換 Fantastic Island 託管模式可用的 YAML 設定檔。";
"Resolved Config File" = "目前設定檔";
"Leave Config File empty if you want Fantastic Island to try to discover a local Mihomo or Clash YAML file automatically." = "如果你不填寫設定檔路徑，Fantastic Island 會嘗試自動發現本機的 Mihomo 或 Clash YAML 設定。";
"Detection Tools" = "探測工具";
"Refresh the detection result or open the API config file that Fantastic Island is currently using." = "刷新探測結果，或直接打開 Fantastic Island 目前使用的 API 設定檔。";
"Managed Tools" = "託管工具";
"Open Fantastic Island's advanced panel, inspect the generated runtime config, or jump to the managed runtime folder." = "打開 Fantastic Island 的進階面板，檢查產生後的執行環境設定，或直接進入託管執行環境目錄。";
"Recent Mihomo runtime output captured while Fantastic Island is managing the built-in runtime." = "這裡顯示 Fantastic Island 託管內建執行環境時捕獲到的最近 Mihomo 輸出。";
"Switch between detection mode and managed mode, then focus on the settings and actions relevant to the mode you picked." = "在探測模式與託管模式之間切換，然後只關注你目前模式真正相關的設定與操作。";
"Network Ports" = "網路埠";
"Fantastic Island only reads the current HTTP, Socks5, and mixed proxy ports from the Clash client you already use." = "Fantastic Island 只會讀取你目前 Clash 客戶端裡的 HTTP、Socks5 與混合代理埠。";
"Managed mode keeps the proxy ports inside Fantastic Island's runtime config so you can align Mihomo with the rest of your network setup." = "託管模式會把代理埠保存在 Fantastic Island 自己的執行環境設定裡，方便你統一管理 Mihomo 的網路入口。";
"Advanced Capabilities" = "進階能力";
"Inspect logs, rules, and connection overview from the detected client without leaving Fantastic Island." = "直接在 Fantastic Island 裡查看探測到的 Clash 客戶端日誌、規則與連線概覽。";
"Inspect runtime logs, current rules, and connection overview for Fantastic Island's managed Mihomo client." = "直接在 Fantastic Island 裡查看託管 Mihomo 的執行日誌、目前規則與連線概覽。";
"Logs" = "日誌";
"Rules" = "規則";
"Connections" = "連線";
"HTTP Proxy Port" = "HTTP 代理埠";
"Socks5 Proxy Port" = "Socks5 代理埠";
"Mixed Proxy Port" = "混合代理埠";
"Detection mode does not rewrite ports. Change them in the Clash client you already run, then let Fantastic Island read the updated values." = "探測模式不會改寫埠。請在你正在使用的 Clash 客戶端裡修改埠，然後讓 Fantastic Island 讀取更新後的值。";
"Ports must be empty or use a value between 1 and 65535." = "埠可以留空，或填寫 1 到 65535 之間的數字。";
"Leave a field empty if you want Fantastic Island to fall back to the generated runtime defaults for that port." = "如果你希望某個埠退回到執行環境設定的預設值，可以把對應輸入框留空。";
